works.description: After giving an exclusive chrome treatment to the Beats by Dr. Dre headphones recently, ColorWare has now announced the availability of the hotly awaited iPad 2. Offered in a wide range of custom colors, the ColorWare custom painted iPad 2 is available with either the gloss finish or a Softouch finish. While a new ColorWare iPad 2 costs $900, you also have the option to send in your iPad 2, and they will color it for $400. On the other hand, the 3G AT&T version will set you back $1030.
